{
  "stem": "19111.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 484.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We should get out-- get out of here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were sure that we were going to get shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "As it turned out, it was that these German soldiers were running away from the front line themselves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so they told us to go in this direction.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Over there, there's a highway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there are Americans over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we didn't believe them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We thought that they were just telling us a story, and they're going to shoot us anyway.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So we ran.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they did not shoot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They took off.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But we knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We knew that it's happening-- just, just a little longer to hold on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And so at that time, it all took a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The next night, we-- my father and I, we were wandering.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And night came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We looked for a place where we can stay overnight.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We found a little cabin from a truck that was stationed-- placed over there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we opened that door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we got inside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we're there through the night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And through the night, there were artillery cannons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Artillery was, was going constantly right over our heads.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And as we woke up in the morning, we-- it was silent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was total silent-- total quiet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And so we started walking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We're just walking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We didn't know where-- what to, to walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We wound up in a little village over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And out of the village came out a, a German in a-- he was in a uniform, and-- one tall German.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And he came to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And he asked us what we're doing here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We told him that we had lost our way, and all that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And he says, you can't come in here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "You can't go here.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
